<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-7815] cqlsh: COPY FROM cannot be interrupted with ctrl-c</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-7815</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The changes in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-7405&quot; title=&quot;Optimize cqlsh COPY TO and COPY FROM&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-7405&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-7405&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; caused the import process to not be interruptable with ctrl-c.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12735868">CASSANDRA-7815</key>
            <summary>cqlsh: COPY FROM cannot be interrupted with ctrl-c</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
